{
  "stem": "3964.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a-- a tremendous amount of harassment of my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were very, very few weeks where the Nazis wouldn't go by our house at night and throw rocks and stones into our windows.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can remember incidents where rocks, like probably weighing two or three pounds, were thrown through our windows and wound up in my bed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very, very scary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I would say that even to this day-- I'm 70 years old-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] if I hear a strange noise at night, I, I have a flashback.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It takes me back to my childhood days, 1933, 1934, and '35 and '36 and '37 when these incidents occurred.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And obviously I know I am here at 1995, and those things couldn't happen here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In any event, my father was kicked out of business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He wasn't kicked out of business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was boycotted to the point that he had to give up his business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he eventually started working for other people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Things became very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The farm, which we had had been worked by us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we always had hired help to do the work my father and mother could not do, weren't able to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "These people who had been working for us were told they could not work any longer for us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had to get rid of our animals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And eventually, we had to get rid of all the farm land we had by literally giving it away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had to sell it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it had to be sold to certain people who were Nazi-- people who were active in the-- in the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were giving preference as far as what land they could buy from Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
